:

1. *Izgovor* je ono što će ti pomoći da se izboriš sa svojim problemima. (The excuse is what will help you to cope with your problems.)

2. Njegov *izgovor* nije bio dovoljno ubedljiv. (His excuse was not convincing enough.)

3. Njen *izgovor* je bio da je zaboravila. (Her excuse was that she forgot.)

4. On se izvinjava zbog njegovog *izgovora*. (He apologizes for his excuse.)

5. Ona nije povjerovala njegovom *izgovoru*. (She didn't believe his excuse.)